data.description: Welcome to 705 Harmony Way in the sought after community of Symphony Village at Centreville.  This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath Vivaldi model home is awaiting it's next owner.  The brick front of the home is just the beginning to the many upgrades that the current owner has added to the home.  As you enter, you'll notice the beautiful hardwood flooring and new carpeting.  The open floorplan with a gas fireplace located on the side of the home allows for an abundance of natural lighting to enter the home.  The gourmet kitchen features granite counters and upgraded stainless appliances.  As you enter the master suite, your eyes will be drawn to the trey ceiling and ceiling fan.  This home offers a unique master bath compared to other homes in the community and features a walk-in shower in place of the corner tub with a dual vanity and linen closet.  The rear of the home features a screened porch with ceiling fan, sun screens and a paver patio.  This home also includes a home generator and portable HVAC unit in the sky basement above the garage.
